//Run Checklist//

Open XAMPP Control Panel.

Start Apache.

Start MySQL.

Open PowerShell in:
C:\xampp\htdocs\sauyo

Start the frontend:

npm.cmd run dev
Look at the terminal and note the exact local URL.
Usually it is:
http://localhost:8080

Open that exact URL in your browser.

If needed, rerun database setup:
http://localhost/sauyo/server/setup-db.php

If login/data does not work

Check MySQL is still running.
Check Apache is still running.
Check the Vite terminal is still open.
Refresh the browser.
If you closed the terminal

Open PowerShell again in C:\xampp\htdocs\sauyo
Run:
npm.cmd run dev

Main URLs
frontend: terminal will show it, usually http://localhost:8080
PHP setup: http://localhost/sauyo/server/setup-db.php